		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Regional Exercise 2012, Mexico&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
